# Summary and Keywords for Toplyne Destination Documentation

**Summary:** This documentation describes the Toplyne destination integration for Amplitude, which helps sales teams at product-led companies convert freemium users by streaming event data from Amplitude to Toplyne, enabling the creation of opportunities in CRMs based on product usage data without engineering involvement.

**Keywords:** Toplyne, event-streaming, sales integration, freemium conversion, product-led growth, CRM opportunities, product usage data, customer segmentation, data science models, pipeline building